posting_body: ['Highline Cherry Creek', '8375 E Yale Avenue, Denver, CO, 80231', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 54', 'OR Text', '54', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team directly.', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'Welcome Home to Highline Cherry Creek', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1036 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Our stylish and beautiful apartment homes offer a range of floor plans including one, two and three- bedroom options.', 'From in-home washers and dryers to wood-style flooring, our apartment interiors combine all the most important features you want.', 'Around the community, you can find a community garden and bike storage, making living even better beyond your front door.', 'Ideally located on East Yale Avenue in Southeast Denver, our community provides you access to dining, shopping, arts, entertainment and recreation.', 'Conveniently located near Denver Tech Center and Tamarac Square, this luxury apartment community puts you in the heart of it all in Denver, allowing you to easily access outdoor spaces such as Cherry Creek State Park and Reservoir.', 'Pet Policy', 'We allow up to three pets and large breeds are welcome too.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sunday: 12:00PM-5:00PM', 'mFsr8tnwqJ9']
